 &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;바포메트 / 제로스 / 데스나이트 / 데몬 / 피닉스</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;거대 드레이크 / &nbsp;발록 / 그림 리퍼 / 아투바 킹 / 분노의 발록</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">4. 보스로부터 획득 가능한 재화류 아이템의 확률이 상향 되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">5. 무한 대전 3/4/5군에서 드랍되는 아데나가 상향되었습니다.&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;1) 3~5군 스테이지 아데나 보상</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;3군: 10,000 아데나&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;4군: 20,000 아데나&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;5군: 35,000 아데나</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; outline: initial;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0);\">* 일부 사냥터 밸런스 조정&nbsp;</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">1. 일부 사냥터 지역의 획득 가능 아이템의 밸런스가 조정되고 드롭 아이템이 추가되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;1) 밸런스 조정 지역</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- 고대 거인의 무덤</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- 상아탑/숨겨진 상아탑</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- 에바/숨겨진 에바 던전</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- 암흑룡의 던전</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;2) 아이템 추가 (소생 포함)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(1) 고대 거인의 무덤</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 마법서(홀리워크:에볼루션), 정령의 수정 (스트라이커 게일:샷), 정령의 수정 (리버레이션)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(2) 상아탑/숨겨진 상아탑</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 마법서 (콜 클랜 어드밴스), 용기사의 서판 (솔리드 노트), 용기사의 서판 (램페이지)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(3) 에바/숨겨진 에바 더전</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 마법서 (이뮨 투 함:세인트), 마법서 (메디테이션:비욘드), 기억의 수정 (본 브레이크:래스트)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(4) 암흑룡의 던전</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 흑정령의 수정 (쉐도우 아머:데스티니), 전사의 인장(버서크), 흑정령의 수정 (무빙 악셀레이션:맥시멈),&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; outline: initial;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0);\">* 그 외&nbsp;</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">1. 혈맹 집결지 던전 4단계까지 돌파 확률을 대폭 상향하였습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">2. 창기사 택티컬 어드밴스의 버프 아이콘이 사라지는 현상이 수정되었습니다. (버프 아이콘만 사라지는 현상, 효과는 적용)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">3. 강화 용기의 물약 사용 가능 클래스에 전사가 추가되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">4. CHA 상승에 따른 특정 스킬 쿨타임 감소가 적용되지 않는 부분이 수정되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">리니지와 함께 즐거운 시간 보내시기 바랍니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">고맙습니다.</div></div>', 0, 1, 'false', NULL);
