(71, 'Metis', '2022-10-13 00:29:56', '10/12 update information', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px ;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0 ); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Eva Kingdom Renewal<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></span>&nbsp;<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. The Eva Kingdom underwater hunting ground has been renewed.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> &nbsp;1) How to enter<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Eva Kingdom Waterway Teleporter<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Eva Kingdom Waterway 3rd floor stairs<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Random non-teleport area<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Random teleportation is possible when possessing the Teleportation Dominance Ring and the Red Knights\' Teleportation Dominance Ring.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter -spacing: 0px !important;\">2. When the Papurion raid appears, the dragon habitat teleporter \'Water Dragon\'s Well\' portal has been changed to appear in the Eva Kingdom.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. The underwater debuff (no breathing) has been changed to be a little more powerful.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Debuff removal item<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Eva\'s Blessing<br style=\"outline: initia