(73, 'Metis', '2022-10-22 02:05:16', '10/19 update information', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px ;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0 ); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Tower of Domination improvements</span></span><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style =\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. The difficulty level of monsters that appear in the Tower of Domination (Inter) has been increased.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. The experience gained when hunting at the Tower of Domination (Inter) has been significantly increased.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. At the Tower of Domination (Inter) The \'Temple of the Ancient Gods\' content that was accessible has been discontinued.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. New items that can be obtained at the top of the Tower of Domination (Inter) have been added.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1) Twilight Pauldrons<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Class: All<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - AC +2<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Close range hit: +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Ranged hit: +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Magic hit: +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Damage reduction: +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - MP absolute recovery: +6 (16 seconds)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - From enchantment +6, per enchantment +1, close range hit +1, ranged hit +1, magic hit +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +7: Add MR +5<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Boots of Solidarity<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Class: All<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - AC -3<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Damage reduction: +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - EXP: +3%<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - EXP +1% per enchantment +1 starting from enchantment +6<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +9: EXP +4%<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Safety enchantment: +4<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. The options for Commander\'s Pauldrons, Saiha\'s Pauldrons, and Archmage\'s Pauldrons have been changed.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Commander\'s Pauldrons<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Class: All<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - AC +0<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Close range hit: +2<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Max MP: +40<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +5: Add HP +50<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +5: PvP damage reduction +3<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +6~+9: PvP damage reduction +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +10: PvP damage reduction +3<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +6~+8: Add HP +10 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +9: Add HP +20<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +10: HP +50<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +5, MP +10 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +7, close range hit +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +5, all resistances +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Shoulder pads<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Class: All<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - AC +0<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Ranged hit: +2<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Max MP: +40<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +5: Add HP +50<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +5: PvP damage reduction +3<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +6~+9: PvP damage reduction +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +10: PvP damage reduction +3<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +6~+8: Add HP +10 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +9: Add HP +20<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +10: HP +50<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +5, MP +10 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +7, ranged hit +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +5, all resistances +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) Archmage\'s Pauldrons<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Class: All<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - AC +0<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Magic hit: +2<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Max MP: +40<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +5: Add HP +50<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +5: PvP damage reduction +3<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +6~+9: PvP damage reduction +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +10: PvP damage reduction +3<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchantment +6~+8: Add HP +10 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +9: Add HP +20<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enchant +10: HP +50<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +5, MP +10 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +7, magic hit +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Starting from enchantment +5, all resistances +1 per enchantment +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Class rebalancing 1st</span></span><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. CON stat HP increase bonus has been increased.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- CON 25: Max HP +50 -&gt; +200<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- CON 35: Max HP +100 -&gt; +400<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- CON 45: Max HP +150 -&gt; +600<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- CON 55: Max HP +200 -&gt; +800<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- CON 60: Max HP +200 -&gt; +1000<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Wizard skills have been rebalanced.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Disintegrate (Nemesis)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Increased average damage<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Divine Protection<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Increased maximum barrier value<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) Fatal Potion<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Increased range: 1 space -&gt; 3 spaces<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;4) Holy Walk<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Add Catalyst: 1 magic stone<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;5) Holy Walk (Evolution)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Catalyst reduction: 2 magic stones -&gt; 1 magic stone<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;6) Eternity<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Average damage slightly reduced<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;7) Heel/Extra Heel/Greater Heel/Full Heel/Heal All<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Cool time slightly increased<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;8) Ice Spike<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Cool time slightly increased<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Warrior skills have been rebalanced.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Titan Bullet<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Increased activation probability<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Titan Magic<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Increased activation probability<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) Titan Rock<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Before change<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Basic activation probability 15%, increases by 2% per 2 levels from level 90, up to 25%<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (2) After change<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Basic activation probability 12%, increases by 2% per 2 levels from level 90, up to 22%<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;4) Howl<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Range reduction: 5 spaces -&gt; 4 spaces<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Damage increase<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;5) Power Grip<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Range reduction: 6 spaces -&gt; 5 spaces<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;6) Tomahawk (Hunter)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Reduces HP absorption<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Inspection skills have been rebalanced.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Phantom (Requiem)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - &nbsp;Strengthens healing recovery reduction effect<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Phantom (Death)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Enhances Death Heal and Death Potion effects<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) Rage<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Slightly reduces activation probability<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* First PC room benefit improvement</span></span><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. PC Play Master UI has been added.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;(*After accessing the PC room, open with the ‘PC’ button or ‘/pc’ command)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) PC room dungeon benefits (provided when accessing the PC room)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Free admission to the Tomb of the Ancient Giants/Tomb of the Ancient Spirits<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (2) 60 minutes of PC room dungeon bonus time added<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (3) PC Room Dungeon Pixie\'s Immortal Protection buff added<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Effect: Prevents experience loss and equipment loss upon death<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Usage restricted for 30 minutes during PK<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (4) Tomb of the Ancient Spirit<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Teleport possible<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Chaotic characters are not allowed to enter<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Increased experience gained<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) PC room benefits (PC Play Master UI)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Advanced Immortal Protection (PC)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Provided 3 times daily (reset at 06:00 daily)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Usage restricted for 30 minutes during PK<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (2) Pixie\'s strengthening magic (120 minutes): Pixie\'s golden feather (PC room: 2 / general: 3)<br style=\"outline: initial ; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(Suspicious Enhancement Wizard Fidor also provides the same buff)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Enchant Dexterity<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Enchant Mighty<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Bless Weapon<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Remove Curse<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- PC room only EXP +10%<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (3) 1st, 3rd, acceleration (60 minutes): Pixie\'s Golden Feather (PC room: 10)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Movement and attack speed increase buff<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3)Pixie\'s golden feather<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Display number of acquisitions today<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (2) Pixie\'s golden feather display<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (3) Adjustment of Pixie\'s golden feather MAX quantity (300)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - The number of feathers exceeding 300 before the update will be maintained.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important ;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Ranking reorganization</span></span><br style =\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. The ranking based on the ranker has been changed.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Before change<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px ! important;\">&nbsp; - 1st ~ 200th place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) After change<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important ;\">&nbsp; - 1st ~ 100th place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Along with the change in rank order, the ranker buff effect has been changed.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) 1st place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: HP +300, AC -4, PvP damage reduction +3, PvP additional damage +3, rank transformation, stat +1, normal protection, 82% weight penalty removed<br style=\"outline: initial; letter -spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) 2nd place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: HP +250, AC -4, PvP damage reduction +2, PvP additional damage +2, rank transformation, stat +1, normal protection, 82% weight penalty removed<br style=\"outline: initial; letter -spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) 3rd place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: HP +250, AC -3, PvP damage reduction +2, PvP additional damage +2, rank transformation, stat +1, normal protection, 82% weight penalty removed<br style=\"outline: initial; letter -spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;4) 4th to 10th place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: HP +200, AC -3, PvP damage reduction +1, PvP additional damage +2, ranking transformation, stat +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> &nbsp;5) 11th to 20th place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: HP +200, AC -3, PvP damage reduction +1, PvP additional damage +2, ranking transformation<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;6) 21st ~ 30th place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: HP +200, AC -3, PvP damage reduction +1, PvP additional damage +2<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;7) 31st place~ 60th place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: HP +200, AC -3, PvP damage reduction +1, PvP additional damage +1<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;8) 61st place~ 100th place<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: HP +200, AC -3, PvP damage reduction +1, EXP +10%<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. The ranker transformation benefit for each class has been changed from 1st to 3rd place for each class to only available for 1st place for each class.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline : initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. The ranking section where the ranker display icon is displayed has been changed.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;(Character selection window and chat window images are separated by section)<br style =\"outline: initial;