(80, 'Metis', '2023-02-02 04:55:41', '2/1 update information', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px ;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0 ); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* General store improvements</span></span><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style= \"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. The items and prices of general stores in each village, siege, and dungeon have been adjusted.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Target NPC<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - General store in each village<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Dragon Dungeon General Store<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Clan gathering place general store<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Forgotten Island General Store<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Glory Hideout General Store<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Oren Ivory Tower 1st floor<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Giran Castle, Oak Fortress, Heine Castle General Store<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Arrogance, Tower of Domination General Store (Supply Manager Rift\'s Support Group, Supply Merchant Chuur)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Sunia, a potion vendor at the Temple of Frost<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2 . The prices