(81, 'Metis', '2023-02-08 23:35:48', '2/8 update information', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px ;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0 ); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Monarch Reboot</span></span><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style= \"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. The following skills of the monarch have been renewed.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; 1) Shining Armor<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Existing<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- ER +10<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (2) Change<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- ER/DG +5, +1 per 2 levels starting from level 90 (maximum +10)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\" ><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Prime<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Changes<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Siege zone effect applies to the caster regardless of region</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple -system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter -spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) Empire<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Changes<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Increased hit probability</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto , Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important ;\">&nbsp;4) Call Clan Advance<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Changes<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Cannot be summoned when hit by a unique class CC</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot ;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline : initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;5) Grace, Shining Shield, Prime<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) Changes<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- If the buff target is in purple state, the caster is also in purple state<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. The monarch\'s new skill has been added.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Brave Union<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Active skill<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Acquisition level: 90<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Consumption: MP 30<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Material: 100 crystals<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Target: The caster and clan members within 8 squares of the party.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: Reduces PvP damage to caster by 5% (regardless of party)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;When the caster is attacked by the PC, the clan members who formed a party within 8 spaces around<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Some damage is shared (2% per person, additional 1% for maximum number of party members, up to 15%)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;If a party member\'s HP is less than 30%, they are excluded from damage distribution<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing : 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Tyrant: Execution<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Passive skill<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Acquisition level: 90<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Target: Speaker<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: Enhanced Tyrant damage<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Gives the target (PC) an attack speed reduction debuff for 4 seconds with a certain probability.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) Conqueror<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Passive skill<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Learning level: 90<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Duration: automatic, always<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Activation condition: Wearing a one-handed sword/dagger<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Target: Speaker<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Effect: After avoiding close range physical attacks with a certain probability, counter attack<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Counter damage is affected by the small monster damage of the sword being worn.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; When a counter is activated, a stun effect is applied to the target with a certain probability<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. New monarch skill acquisition location has been added.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Magic Book (Brave Union), Magic Book (Brave Union) (Revival)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Zeros, Great Black Elder, Doppelganger Boss<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Magic Book (Tyrant: Execution), Magic Book (Tyrant: Execution) (Revival)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Kurtz, Death Knight, Warden Taros<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) Magic Book (Conqueror), Magic Book (Conqueror) (Revival)<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Halfas, Balakas, Furious Balrog<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. The appearance of the monarch ranker transformation has been renewed.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot ;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Hidden Hunting Ground Boost Mode</span></span><br style=\"outline: initial;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"> 1. Hidden hunting ground Boost area has been added.<br style=\"outline: initial;\">&nbsp;1) Hidden hunting ground Boost list<br style=\"outline: initial;\">&nbsp; - Hidden Ivory Tower Boost <br style=\"outline: initial;\">&nbsp; - Hidden Land of the Forsaken Boost<br style=\"outline: initial;\">&nbsp; - Hidden Eva Kingdom Waterway Boost<br style=\" outline: initial;\">&nbsp; - Hidden Ivory Tower Boost<br style=\"outline: initial;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\">&nbsp;2) Hidden Hunting Ground Boost<br style= \"outline: initial;\">&nbsp; - 4 hidden dimension hourglasses: recharge for 1 hour (requires 4 hourglasses of the same type)<br style=\"outline: initial;\">&nbsp; - recharge Method: Double-click the hourglass in the hidden dimension, select the Hidden Hunting Ground (Boost) item, and charge<br style=\"outline: initial;\">&nbsp; - Charge for up to 12 hours per week per character<br style=\" outline: initial;\">&nbsp; - Boost regions have higher rewards and rewards than regular regions</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot; , &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial;\">We hope you have a great time with Lineage.</div><div data- contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Thank you.</div></div>', 3, 1, 'false', NULL),
