(84, 'Metis', '2023-03-29 19:14:48', '3/29 update information', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px ;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0 ); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Class Reboot - Dragon Knight</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font -family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font- size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font -family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">1.&nbsp;The Dragon Knight Ranker transformation appearance has been renewed.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, - apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">2. The effect of the Dragon Knight\'s \'Weakness Exposure\' debuff has been changed.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font- family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Existing: Duration 16 seconds, debuff ends when Poe Slayer is used once</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\" font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- Changed: Duration 8 seconds, debuff does not end even when using Poe Slayer</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style= \"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">Applies AC +5, DG -10, and Verbal Resistance -10 to target</div><div data-contents-type =\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, - apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">3. The following skills of the Dragon Knight have been renewed.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) Halfpas<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Existing: Duration 300 seconds, MP consumption 18<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Change: Duration 600 seconds, MP consumption 30<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) Destroy<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Existing: Duration 16 seconds, AC+10<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Changes: individual cooldown, duration 8 seconds, increased hit chance, AC+5<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) Destroy: Peer<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Existing: Target DG-20<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Change: Target\'s DG-10<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;4) Thunder Grab<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Existing: Duration 1~4 seconds<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Change: Increased cooldown, duration 2-3 seconds, increased hit probability<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;5) Thunder Grab: Brave<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Existing: Thunder Grab\'s hold duration increased to 3~6 seconds<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Change: Thunder Grab\'s hold duration increased to 3~4 seconds<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;6) Poe Slayer: Brave<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; - Slightly reduces stun duration<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, - apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">4.&nbsp;The Dragon Knight\'s new skills have been added.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple -system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;1) Poe Slayer: Force</div ><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Passive skills</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Acquisition level: 90</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Effect: Increases Poe Slayer stun duration by 1 second, increases activation probability</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Cannot be dispelled or reflected by recovery or Maelstrom skills</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;2) Chain Reaction</div ><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Active Skill</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Cooldown: Individual</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Acquisition level: 90</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Consumption: MP 15, HP 15</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system , BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Material: 1 engraved bone fragment</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple- system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Target: 1 PC within 4 spaces</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple- system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Effect: Stun, increases the duration of the target (PC) by 1 second (probability)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\" >&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;When the chain reaction effect is activated, powerful damage occurs to the target</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot ;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Recovery, cannot be canceled or reflected by Maelchrome skills</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot; , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;3) Behemoth</div ><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Active Skill</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Cooldown: Individual</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;NotoSans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Acquisition level: 90</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot ;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Consumption: MP 30</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot ;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Material: 2 engraved bone fragments</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Target: Including PCs within 4 spaces, all PCs within 1 space around it</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\" font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Effect: Deals powerful damage to all enemies (PC) within 1 space, including the specified target,</div><div data-contents-type=\"text \" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The caster immediately recovers HP equal to 40% of the damage inflicted by enemies (maximum 2000)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hit enemies have a certain probability of not being able to return (can move) + reduced movement speed</div><div data- contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, - apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">5.&nbsp;A new skill acquisition location for the Dragon Knight has been added.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;1) Dragon Knight\'s Tablet (Chain Reaction), Dragon Knight\'s Tablet (Chain Reaction) (Revival)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Zeros, Great Black Elder, Akhmo</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;2) Tablet of the Dragon Knight (Foe Slayer: Force), Tablet of the Dragon Knight (Foe Slayer: Force) (Revival)</div><div data-contents-type= \"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Lindvior, Pafurion, Antharas</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot; Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;3) Dragon Knight\'s Tablet (Behemoth), Dragon Knight\'s Tablet (Behemoth) (Revival)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style= \"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Halfas, Balakas, Furious Balrog</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot ;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, - apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, - apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Add mythic weapon&nbsp;</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, - apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">1.&nbsp;Mythic weapon&nbsp;\'Auracia\'s Transcendence\' has been added.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\" font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;1) Transcendence of Auracia</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot; Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Equipped Class: Dragon Knight</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Material: Duranium</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot ;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Damage: 46/40, non-damaging</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - STR +3</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot; Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Close range damage +35, close range hit +17, close range critical hit +7</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font -family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - verb hit +15</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot ;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Magic activation: Auracia\'s Strike (PvP), Auracia\'s Wrath (PvE)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style =\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Enchantment options</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Per +1